osvSchema.details: Dell PowerEdge BIOS contains an improper privilege management security vulnerability. An unauthenticated local attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to privilege escalation.

description_data.value: Dell PowerEdge BIOS contains an improper privilege management security vulnerability. An unauthenticated local attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to privilege escalation.

description.value: CWE-306: Missing Authentication for Critical Function

descriptions.value: Dell PowerEdge BIOS contains an improper privilege management security vulnerability. An unauthenticated local attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to privilege escalation.

Dell PowerEdge BIOS contiene una vulnerabilidad de seguridad de administración de privilegios inadecuada. Un atacante local no autenticado podría explotar esta vulnerabilidad, lo que provocaría una escalada de privilegios.
